CIMIOTTI UNHAIRING CO. et al. v. SCHULANG. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. October 29, 1903.) No. 11. Appeal from the Circuit Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. Theodore B. Chancello, for appellant. Louis C. Raegener, for appellees.

Before WALLACE, TOWNSEND, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

No opinion. Order reversed in open court.
